According to the SAPS, a man was defrauded out of R51 000 during a sales transaction. The complainant paid the sum of money in question, into an account during the purchase of a vehicle. The vehicle was never delivered to the complainant, and the suspect disappeared after the transaction. It is believed that the woman, only known an Nchabeleng, is located in the Middelburg area. Anyone with more information on the whereabouts of Nchabeleng is asked to contact the investigating officer, Detective Mdluli, on 060 656 7118 or 013 249 1402/1600.